event AccPnlPerTokenUsedUpdated(address indexed sender, uint256 indexed newEpoch, uint256 prevPositiveOpenPnl, uint256 newPositiveOpenPnl, uint256 newEpochPositiveOpenPnl, int256 newAccPnlPerTokenUsed)
event AssetsReceived(address indexed sender, address indexed user, uint256 assets, uint256 assetsLessDeplete)
event AssetsSent(address indexed sender, address indexed receiver, uint256 assets)
event Depleted(address indexed sender, uint256 assets, uint256 amountTizz)

event DepositLocked(address indexed sender, address indexed owner, uint256 depositId, tuple(address owner, uint256 shares, uint256 assetsDeposited, uint256 assetsDiscount, uint256 atTimestamp, uint256 lockDuration) d)

event DepositUnlocked(address indexed sender, address indexed receiver, address indexed owner, uint256 depositId, tuple(address owner, uint256 shares, uint256 assetsDeposited, uint256 assetsDiscount, uint256 atTimestamp, uint256 lockDuration) d)
event Refilled(address indexed sender, uint256 assets, uint256 amountTizz)
event RewardDistributed(address indexed sender, uint256 assets)
event TizzPriceProviderUpdated(tuple(address addr, bytes signature) newValue)
event WithdrawCanceled(address indexed sender, address indexed owner, uint256 shares, uint256 currEpoch, uint256 indexed unlockEpoch)
event WithdrawRequested(address indexed sender, address indexed owner, uint256 shares, uint256 currEpoch, uint256 indexed unlockEpoch)
function getLockedDeposit(uint256 depositId) view returns (tuple(address owner, uint256 shares, uint256 assetsDeposited, uint256 assetsDiscount, uint256 atTimestamp, uint256 lockDuration))
function updateAccPnlPerTokenUsed(uint256 prevPositiveOpenPnl, uint256 newPositiveOpenPnl) returns (uint256)
